Class DefaultStatisticsFormatter

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class DefaultStatisticsFormatter
extends Object
implements StatisticsFormatter
    Default StatisticsFormatter that has no header or footer and delegates all formatting to a GroupedTimingStatisticsFormatter.
